  <title>EVENT(Add 和 Remove)))</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>ADD</keyword>
    <keyword>EVENT</keyword>
    <keyword>REMOVE</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">EVENT(Add 和 Remove)))</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">XSharp 现在支持扩展的 &quot;EVENT &quot;语法。既支持单行语法，也支持多行语法：</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">旧语法</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">[Attributes] [Modifiers] EVENT [&lt;ExplicitInterface&gt;.] &lt;Id&gt; AS &lt;Type&gt; &#160; &#160;// 旧语法</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">带有明确表达式的单行语法</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">[Attributes] [Modifiers] EVENT [&lt;ExplicitInterface&gt;.] &lt;Id&gt; AS &lt;Type&gt; &#160; [ADD &lt;ExpressionList] [REMOVE &lt;ExpressionList] &#160; // 单行</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">带有明确表达式的多行语法</para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example">[Attributes] [Modifiers] EVENT [&lt;ExplicitInterface&gt;.] &lt;Id&gt; AS &lt;Type&gt; &#160; &#160; // 多行<br/><br/>ADD<br/> &#160; &#160;&lt;Statements&gt;<br/>END [ADD]<br/>REMOVE<br/> &#160; &#160;&lt;Statements&gt;<br/>END [REMOVE]<br/>END [EVENT]</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">示例 </para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><snippet src="Ex-EVENT" inline="false"/></para>
  </body>
